Genova Inc said it signed adefinitive agreement for the previously announced merger with&lt;Genova Products Inc>.    Under the agreement, Genova Products will pay 5-3/8 dlrs ashare for the 29 pct of Genova's outstanding common shares itdoes not already own.    The company said it plans to complete the transaction,which requires shareholder approval, by the end of March. Reuter&#3;